      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "1. An access ID is equivalent to an image input.\n2. For the first frame, if you use an access ID input, you cannot use an image input simultaneously. The same applies to the last frame.\n3. You don't need to use the asset ID for both the first and last frames. This workflow is just an example of how to use real human assets."
