      "widgets_values": [
        "Seedance 2.0",
        "[Style] Futuristic magical water observatory, 8K ultra-clear, Photorealistic, High-fashion Editorial, circular fountain platform, suspended liquid membranes, aurora color gradients, dreamlike sci-fi elegance, Unreal Engine 5 fluid simulation and atmospheric glow.\n\nProtagonist note:\nA female fashion model, mid-20s, editorial silhouette: shoulder-length auburn hair in loose waves, tall lean build, calm confident posture.\n\n[Duration] 5 seconds.\n\n[Scene] A circular observatory suspended above a dark luminous void; a ring-shaped fountain surrounds the platform; thin vertical water membranes hover like transparent walls, and the ceiling glows with aurora colors.\n\n[00:00-00:02] Shot 1: Fountain ring.\nCamera: medium-wide orbit around the circular platform; water ring and figure share the frame.\nAction: She walks along the fountain rim; the thin water membranes around the platform shimmer with the ceiling colors.\nEffect: The nearest water membranes begin to peel away from the fountain ring into soft liquid sheets that resemble miniature aurora walls.\n\n[00:02-00:04] Shot 2: Membrane rise.\nCamera: medium three-quarter on torso, the fountain rim, and nearby water curtain.\nAction: She raises both hands slowly.\nEffect: The liquid membranes peel fully away from the fountain ring and rise into tall aurora-tinted sheets, matching the observatory geometry.\n\n[00:04-00:05] Shot 3: Observatory dissolve.\nCamera: crane up into a top view of the circular space.\nAction: She remains in the center while the sheets expand beyond her.\nEffect: The fountain ring, floor circle, and hovering water walls all soften into luminous aurora washes, and the observatory disappears into a vast magical liquid sky.",
        "480p",
        "16:9",
        7,
        true,
        0,
        "randomize",
        false,
        "",
        ""
